{
  "stem": "8775.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I forgot to mention that there was a nice river called Tiza, T-I-Z-A River, by Szolnok.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was a nice park by the river, so we would walk there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And everybody knew that the Soltis were on a stroll, on a leisurely stroll, in the evening hours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this was a leisurely time for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But after the 1940s, I noticed that my parents started to close themselves in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were whispering among themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were listening to the BBC, the British Broadcasting, n, in German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were not open and frank about what's happening in the world around us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The Hungarian Jews, we are pretty, well, I don't know if this is the word, naive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They believed very much in it that they, they are somewhat better then perhaps the Polish or the, or the Russian Jews, by virtue of their assimilation to the general Hungarian public.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They acted out and they, they worked like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They had their businesses, like professions, and their stores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there was really not that much of a discrimination before 1940.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And-- like, not as I know of.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And later on, it has all changed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[COUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, my parents explained it to me, that things are not going well for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm not sure if they talked too much about Hitler's rise to power.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they just-- they were very protective of me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said well, stay away from them, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't cause any problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't go where these guys are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Stay away from the ice skating rink.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so then we started to, to just do in-house plays.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got together with friends and played Monopoly and indoor games.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would not go out to the streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
